    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="class_kokkos_1_1_scope_guard" kindref="compound">ScopeGuard</ref> Some user scope issues have been identified with some Kokkos::finalize calls; <ref refid="class_kokkos_1_1_scope_guard" kindref="compound">ScopeGuard</ref> aims to correct these issues. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Two requirements for <ref refid="class_kokkos_1_1_scope_guard" kindref="compound">ScopeGuard</ref>: if Kokkos::is_initialized() in the constructor, don&apos;t call Kokkos::initialize or Kokkos::finalize it is not copyable or assignable </para>
